on x86 client
-------------

	#apt-get install tightvnc-viewer


on BBB 
------

	#apt-get install tighvncserver

after installation setup the server

	#tightvncserver
	Password:	//give a password
	verify: 	//verify by retyping the same password
	viewonly password(y/n): y
	
running the vnc server 
	vncserver :1 -geometry 1280x800 -depth 24 -dpi 96
	
